Name: Power
Note: 回傳Template command. CMD3, CMD4, CMD5與Get command的CMD3, CMD4, CMD5相同. CMD6, CMD7, CMD8格式與Set command 相同

Name: Home Key Event
Note:
Reply CMD8:
0x31 ->Power key long press
0x30 ->Not event triggered

Name: Get Current Game/Pro. Mode
Note:
Reply CMD7:
0x30 ->Game mode
0x31 ->Profession mode
Reply CMD8:
Game mode: USER->0x30, FPS->0x31, Racing ->0x32, RTS->3, RPG->0x34, Premium Color -> 0x35
Profession mode: USER -> 0x30, Anti-Blue ( Reader ) -> 0x31, Movie ( Cinema ) -> 0x32, Office ( Designer ) -> 0x33, sRGB -> 0x34, Adobe RGB -> 0x35, Display P3 -> 0x36, Eco -> 0x37
例如:
當Monitor mode為Racing mode，使用Get current Game/Pro. Mode得到回傳值為CMD7: 0x30, CMD8: 0x32
當Monitor mode為Eco mode，使用Get current Game/Pro. Mode得到回傳值為CMD7: 0x31, CMD8: 0x37

Name: Get Current Model Index
Note:
Reply CMD8: 0x30 ->MPG27C (Scaler NT68875)
0x31 ->MPG27CQ (Scaler NT68394)
0x32 ->MAG241C
0x33 ->MAG271C
0x34 ->MAG241CR
0x35 ->MAG271CR
0x36 ->MAG271CQR
0x37 -> MPG271C
0x38 -> MPG271CQ
0x39 -> MPG27CQ2
0x3A -> MAG321CQR
0x3B -> MAG321CUR
0x3C -> MAG271R
0x3D -> MAG322CQR
0x3E -> MPG341CQR
0x3F -> PS341WU
0x40 -> MAG271V

Name: Get EDID SN
Note:
SN Number is 13 characters.
(Reply special command)
CMD6 -> SN0,… CMD18 -> SN12
